src:
Gorelo osebno vozilo
03 Nov 2019, 07:00 by M. Ž.
Na Maistrovi ulici v Brežicah je na parkirišču malo po četrti uri zjutraj zagorelo osebno vozilo. Požar so pogasili gasilci PGD Brežice. Obveščene so bile pristojne službe.
Sinoči, okoli devete ure zvečer pa je v Župelevcu v občini Brežice gorela vsebina v treh zabojnikih za smeti. Požar so pogasili gasilci PGD Župelevec in Kapele.
text:
Burned passenger car
03 Nov 2019, 07:00 by M. Ž.
On Maistrova Street in Brežice, a car was set on fire in the parking lot just after four o'clock in the morning. The fire was extinguished by the fire brigade PGD Brezice. The competent services were informed.
Last night, around nine o'clock in the evening, the contents in three garbage cans burned in Zupelevac in the municipality of Brežice. The fire was extinguished by firefighters PGD Župelevec and Kapele.
